# =========================================================
#                CONCEPT OF RULE-BASED CHATBOT
# =========================================================

# A Rule-Based Chatbot works on fixed conditions written
# by the programmer.

# It does not learn automatically like Machine Learning
# models.

# The chatbot checks user responses and matches them
# with predefined rules.

# Example:
# IF fever = yes AND cough = yes
# THEN suggest Flu.

# Rule-based chatbots are:
# 1. Easy to build
# 2. Fast
# 3. Beginner-friendly
# 4. Suitable for simple applications

# However, they:
# 1. Cannot understand complex sentences
# 2. Cannot learn from experience
# 3. Work only on predefined rules


